                           Sort Key: sorted_merge_test.id
                           Sort Method: top-N heapsort  Memory: NkB
                           ->  Seq Scan on public.sorted_merge_test_960000 sorted_merge_test (actual rows=N loops=N)
                                 Output: id
(20 rows)

